         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Chief Secretary's Office ¶ Melbourne 27 July 1871. ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ I have the honor to enclose a letter to Mr Ferguson returning him his report on the State Forests for 1870, and directing him to forward ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">71.07.27b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From William Odgers</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 2465, unit 26, pp. 156-7, VPRS 1187/P outward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Chief Secretary's Office</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne 27 July 1871.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to enclose a letter to Mr Ferguson returning him his report on the State Forests for 1870, and directing him to forward it in the regular official manner.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You will be good enough to cause it to be delivered to Mr Ferguson; instructing the messenger who hands it to him to report to you the hour he does so.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M to C. Gavan Duffy, July 1871, registered on 27 July 1871,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>indicated that the Forest Inspector, William Ferguson, had submitted his report<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>direct<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>to the Lands Department. In a previous letter to the former Chief Secretary M had <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>complained that Ferguson was bypassing him in communicating to Government (M to James McCulloch 15 June 1871).<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>There had been similar difficulties earlier in the year concerning Ferguson suppling fish from a pond in teh gardens to the Lands Department (M to C. Hodgkinson, 25 March 1871).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Your most obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>W. H. Odgers</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The Director</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Botanic Gardens.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
